<section id="layanan" class="visual-feature">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="feature-intro">
      <h2 class="fade-in-on-scroll">Jasa Bore Pile Berpengalaman - Hadiwijaya Bore Pile</h2>
      <p class="fade-in-on-scroll">Cari jasa bore pile yang termurah, tapi takut dikerjakan asal-asalan? Bagaimana jika dana membengkak karena dikerjakan oleh amatiran? Bagaimana jika proyek ini terhenti karena masalah teknis? Kekhawatiran ini bukan sekadar hal teknis. Ini adalah ketakutan akan kegagalan, kehilangan waktu, dan kerugian finansial yang tak terbayangkan. Bersama kami, mari kita menyelam ke bawah tanah, memahami seluk beluk pondasi bore pile yang kuat dan efisien. Luangkan waktu sejenak, kami akan bahas tuntas sampai ke dasar.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bore-pile-explanation fade-in-on-scroll">
      <div class="explanation-text">
        <h3>Apa Itu Bore Pile?</h3>
        <p>Bore pile adalah pondasi yang menancap jauh ke dalam tanah, mencari lapisan terkuat untuk menopang beban bangunan. Ini bukan hanya soal mengebor lubang, tapi tentang ilmu di balik bangunan yang kokoh.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="explanation-diagram">
        <img src="/assets/img/bore.png" alt="Diagram Penampang Bore Pile" class="bore-pile-image">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tools-comparison">
      <h3 class="fade-in-on-scroll">Jenis Alat Bore Pile untuk Setiap Kebutuhan Proyek</h3>
      <p class="fade-in-on-scroll">Setiap lokasi proyek memiliki ceritanya sendiri. Itu sebabnya kami menyediakan solusi yang tepat, bukan sekadar satu metode untuk semua.</p>
      
      <div class="tools-grid stagger-children">
        <!-- Kartu 1: Manual -->
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-header">
              <img src="/assets/svg/straus.svg" alt="Icon Strauss Pile" class="card-icon" />
              <h4>Alat Bore Pile Manual (Strauss Pile)</h4>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Cocok untuk:</strong> Proyek kecil seperti rumah tinggal di area padat.</p>
            <div class="charts">
              <div class="chart-item">
                <span>Biaya</span>
                <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar" style="width: 25%;"></div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="chart-item">
                <span>Kekuatan & Kedalaman</span>
                <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar" style="width: 35%;"></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact?subject=Info%20Bore%20Pile%20Manual" class="cta-card">Pilih Metode Manual</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Kartu 2: Mini Crane -->
        <div class="tool-card active">
           <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-header">
              <img src="/assets/svg/minicrane.svg" alt="Icon Mini Crane" class="card-icon" />
              <h4>Alat Mesin Mini Crane (Gawangan)</h4>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Cocok untuk:</strong> Ruko atau gudang di area sempit dengan akses terbatas.</p>
            <div class="charts">
              <div class="chart-item">
                <span>Biaya</span>
                <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar" style="width: 50%;"></div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="chart-item">
                <span>Kekuatan & Kedalaman</span>
                <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar" style="width: 65%;"></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact?subject=Info%20Bore%20Pile%20Mini%20Crane" class="cta-card cta-main">Solusi Paling Populer</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Kartu 3: Drilling Rig -->
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-header">
              <img src="/assets/svg/hydraulic.svg" alt="Icon Hydraulic Drilling Rig" class="card-icon" />
              <h4>Alat Berat Bore Pile (Drilling Rig)</h4>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Cocok untuk:</strong> Proyek skala besar seperti gedung bertingkat dan jembatan.</p>
            <div class="charts">
              <div class="chart-item">
                <span>Biaya</span>
                <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar" style="width: 90%;"></div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="chart-item">
                <span>Kekuatan & Kedalaman</span>
                <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar" style="width: 100%;"></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact?subject=Info%20Bore%20Pile%20Alat%20Berat" class="cta-card">Konsultasi Proyek Besar</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Post-grid CTA -->
      <div class="post-grid-cta fade-in-on-scroll">
        <p>Bingung memilih metode bore pile yang tepat? <strong>Kami siap membantu.</strong></p>
        <a href="/contact?subject=Konsultasi%20Metode%20Bore%20Pile" class="cta-button">Konsultasi Gratis Sekarang !!!</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .visual-feature {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background-color: var(--background-color);
  }
  .visual-feature .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
  }
  .feature-intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;
  }
  .feature-intro h2 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .feature-intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
  }

  .bore-pile-explanation {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .explanation-text h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .explanation-text p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
  }
  .explanation-diagram {
    align-self: center;
    justify-self: center;
  }
  .bore-pile-image {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .tools-comparison {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .tools-comparison h3 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .tools-comparison > p {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
    color: #555;
  }
  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: stretch; 
  }
  .tool-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .card-content {
    flex-grow: 1; 
  }
  .tool-card:hover, .tool-card.active {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(34, 42, 122, 0.15);
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
  }
  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start; 
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    min-height: 80px; 
  }
  .card-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .tool-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .tool-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #444;
  }
  .charts {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .chart-item {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .chart-item span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .bar-container {
    width: 100%;
    height: 12px;
    background: #e0e5ee;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bar {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), #ff8c42);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .cta-card {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: #e9ecef;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-sizing: border-box; 
  }
  .cta-card:hover {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    color: white;
  }
  .cta-card.cta-main {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
  }
  .cta-card.cta-main:hover {
    background: #e65200;
  }

  .post-grid-cta {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .post-grid-cta p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .post-grid-cta .cta-button {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
  }
  .post-grid-cta .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .post-grid-cta {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .post-grid-cta p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .feature-intro h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .bore-pile-explanation {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>